253
00:13:43,550 --> 00:13:46,960
Ngunit kilala si Matandang Guro Xue.

254
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:50,320
Natatakot akong
mga mayayamang pamilya lang ang maaaring mag-imbita sa kanya.

255
00:13:52,630 --> 00:13:53,690
Magbabakasyon na ako.

256
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:58,510
Nay, pupunta po ako sa Ikapitong Lola.

257
00:13:58,510 --> 00:14:00,910
Hindi siya uupo lang at manunuod.

258
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,750
Sasama ako kay Zhen.

259
00:14:10,380 --> 00:14:11,170
Tulong!

260
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,320
Buksan mo ang pinto! May tao ba diyan?

261
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:15,630
May tao ba riyan? Pakiusap, iligtas mo ang aking ama!

262
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,750
Young Master Zhengliang

263
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:21,600
