264
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,390
Ginoong Zhou,

265
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:23,920
Malubha ang sakit ng aking ama.

266
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:27,080
Kailangan natin ang Ikapitong Lola
para imbitahan si Matandang Guro Xue.

267
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:29,270
Pakitingnan po sana namin ang Ikapitong Lola.

268
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:31,750
Ginoong Zhou, nagmamakaawa po ako sa inyo.

269
00:14:32,110 --> 00:14:34,480
Iligtas mo po ang aking ama.

270
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:35,240
Sige.

271
00:14:35,550 --> 00:14:37,240
Papasok ako at iaanunsyo ko sa iyo.

272
00:14:37,270 --> 00:14:38,150
Sandali lang.

273
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:39,510
Huminto.

274
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,360
Hindi ka makakapunta.

275
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,670
Lumabas ka!

276
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:03,960
