277
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,390
Dapat ay maayos na siya ngayon.

278
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,910
Yung Tian Jiangyue.

279
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,120
Usapin ito ng buhay at kamatayan.

280
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,650
Paano niya nagawang gawin ang ganoong bagay?

281
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,080
Doktor Xue,

282
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:16,510
Kumusta na siya?

283
00:15:16,510 --> 00:15:18,840
Ikapitong Matandang Ginang, Unang Batang Ginang,

284
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:20,080
Huli na ako nang isang hakbang.

285
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:22,720
Kung
naibigay sana ang matapang na gamot nang mas maaga,

286
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:24,850
marahil ay nakayanan niya sana.

287
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,910
Sa huli...

288
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:37,270
huli na ang lahat.

289
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:39,870
Jingfu?

290
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,240
Jingfu?

291
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,480
Anak ko,

292
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:04,440
Hindi kita sinisisi.

293
00:16:10,590 --> 00:16:11,760
Hindi kita sinisisi.

294
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:24,720
Jingfu.

295
00:16:25,510 --> 00:16:26,510
Jingfu.

296
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:30,240
Hindi ba't sinabi mong ibabalik mo kami
sa Yi County?

297
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:33,840
Sabi mo doon ako lumaki.

298
00:16:34,630 --> 00:16:36,510
Nangako ka sa amin.

299
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:39,480
Ama.

300
00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:40,320
Jingfu,

301
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:42,080
kung aalis ka,

302
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:45,740
Sino ang mag-aalaga kina Zhen,
Zhengliang, at sa akin?

303
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,440
Jingfu!

304
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:49,360
Ama,

305
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:52,720
Hindi ba dumating si Doktor Xue?

306
00:16:52,870 --> 00:16:55,270
Tiyak na kaya ka niyang gamutin.

307
00:16:56,670 --> 00:16:58,000
Ama!

308
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,510
Jingfu!

309
00:17:00,790 --> 00:17:02,240
Jingfu!

310
00:17:19,970 --> 00:17:25,770
[Libingan ni Li Jingfu]

311
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,070
Ina,

312
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:34,000
dahil lang sa
tinanggal ang aming mga pangalan sa talaan ng pamilya,

313
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:37,280
Ibig sabihin ba niyan ay
hindi na tayo bahagi ng pamilyang Li?

314
00:17:40,270 --> 00:17:41,960
Kahit hindi tayo pamilya,

315
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,880
bilang isang tao sa isa pa,

316
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:46,310
paano nila nagawang panoorin na lang siyang mamatay?

317
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:50,720
Zhen.

318
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:53,510
Magkakaiba ang bawat tao.

319
00:17:55,070 --> 00:17:56,670
Pero hindi natin kontrolado ang iba.

320
00:17:58,160 --> 00:17:59,620
Dapat nating isagawa ang ating mga sarili

321
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:01,480
para makasagot tayo sa langit at lupa,

322
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:03,030
at sa ating sariling mga konsensya.

323
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:06,400
Mula ngayon,

324
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,290
kalimutan mo na ang bahay na 'yan.

325
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:10,480
Ito na ang tahanan namin ngayon.

326
00:18:11,070 --> 00:18:12,130
Naiintindihan mo ba?

327
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,000
Oo.

328
00:18:15,590 --> 00:18:16,200
Sige.

329
00:18:16,310 --> 00:18:17,240
Huwag kang umiyak.

330
00:18:18,350 --> 00:18:19,080
Tumigil ka na sa pag-iyak.

331
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:21,750
Bukas,

332
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:24,070
Maglalagay ako ng higaan ng uod na seda dito.

333
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:25,440
Mag-alaga tayo ng mga silkworm.

334
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,830
Kapag lumaki na ang mga silkworm

335
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,210
at iikot ang kanilang mga cocoon,

336
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:32,110
Kaya kong gumawa ng bagong damit para sa iyo

337
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:34,750
at isang bagong pares ng sapatos para sa iyong kapatid.

338
00:18:35,350 --> 00:18:38,240
Pero kailangan mo akong tulungan
sa pamimitas ng mga dahon ng mulberry.

339
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:39,160
Okay?

340
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,310
Sige.

341
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:43,070
Maglalagay din tayo ng kama na gawa sa kawayan

342
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:44,350
sa labas ng bahay.

343
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:47,880
Maaari nating panoorin ang buwan sa taglagas,
ang niyebe sa taglamig,

344
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:50,720
at tamasahin ang malamig na hangin sa tag-araw.

345
00:18:51,350 --> 00:18:52,950
Makakapanood pa nga tayo ng mga alitaptap.

346
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:54,110
Tingnan mo.

347
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:55,760
May bakanteng lote doon.

348
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:58,110
Plano kong magtanim ng ilang gulay

349
00:18:58,160 --> 00:19:00,690
at pag-aalaga ng ilang manok,
pato, at gansa.

350
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:03,790
Magtatanim din ako ng mga bulaklak ng balsamo

351
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,550
sa labas ng pader ng patyo

352
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:07,640
para pinturahan ang iyong mga kuko.

353
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:08,550
Ina.

354
00:19:09,480 --> 00:19:11,200
Gusto kong kumain ng ubas.

355
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:12,510
Sigurado.

356
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,400
Pagkatapos...

357
00:19:14,960 --> 00:19:15,750
Sa labas,

358
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:17,880
maglalagay tayo ng trellis

359
00:19:18,350 --> 00:19:20,030
at magtanim ng mga ubas para sa iyo.

360
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:25,680
Ina,

361
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,640
lahat ba ng sinabi mo

362
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:29,350
nagkatotoo ba talaga?

363
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:30,480
Siyempre.

364
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:33,000
Tiyak na mangyayari iyon.

365
00:19:33,350 --> 00:19:34,350
Pangako ko sa iyo.

366
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:36,070
Tara na.

367
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:54,270
